properties.Name: InsuranceDiscountType
properties.Description:
A type of insurance discount that may be applied to the insurance product.

Boat Ex:
- Coast Guard Certification Discount
- Diesel Engine Discount
- Multi-policy Discount
- Protective Devices Discount

Condominium Ex:
- 55 and Retired Discount
- Age of construction discount
- Age of insured discount
- Claims-free discount
- Deadlock bolts
- Fire alarm system
- Fire extinguishers in condo
- Home + Auto discount
- Home and car discount
- Protective device
- Security system
- Smoke detectors
- Vault 

Earthquake Ex:
- Age of Home Discount
- Construction Type Discount
- Fire Safety Equipment Discount
- Gas Shutoff Safety Equipment Discount
- Location Discount
- Retrofit Discount

Flood Ex:
- NFIP Participation Discount
- Community Rating System (CRS) Program Discount

Where:

NFIP PARTICIPATION DISCOUNT
Residents in unincorporated areas of Carroll County, Maryland, will receive a 10 percent reduction in their flood insurance premiums, effective October 1, 2007, because their community now participates in floodplain management measures encouraged by the National Flood Insurance Program (NFIP).

Homeowners Ex:
- Deadlock bolts
- Fire alarm system
- Fire extinguishers in the home
- Security system
- Smoke detectors

Motorcycle Ex:
- 50+ Driver 
- Accident Free Discount
- Anti-Theft Device Discount
- Defensive Driver Course
- Driver Education
- Driver Training
- Multi-vehicle discount:
- Seasonal Use Discount

Personal Umbrella Liability Ex:
- 50+ Age Discount
- Home and Car Discount
- Multi-policy discount

Recreational Vehicle (RV) Ex:
- 50+ Driver Discount

- Carpool Discount
- Driver Education
- Driver Training
- Home and Car Discount
- Homeowners policy discount
- Multi-vehicle discount:

Renters Ex:

- Air Bag Discount
- Anti-Theft Device Discount
- Carpool Discount
